        public POSTaggerAnnotator(String posLoc,
                  boolean verbose,
                  int maxSentenceLength,
                  int numThreads)
        Create a POS tagger annotator.
        Parameters:
        posLoc - Location of POS tagger model (may be file path, classpath resource, or URL
        verbose - Whether to show verbose information on model loading
        maxSentenceLength - Sentences longer than this length will be skipped in processing
        numThreads - The number of threads for the POS tagger annotator to use
